an class=\"token punctuation\">,</span> <span class=\"token string\">\"bar\"</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n\nwm<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span><span class=\"token function\">has</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span>obj<span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span> <span class=\"token comment\">// true</span>\nwm<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span><span class=\"token function\">has</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span>window<span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span> <span class=\"token comment\">// true</span>\n\nwm<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span><span class=\"token function\">clear</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n\nwm<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span><span class=\"token function\">has</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span>obj<span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span>  <span class=\"token comment\">// false</span>\nwm<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span><span class=\"token function\">has</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span>window<span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span>  <span class=\"token comment\">// false</span>\n</code></pre></div>","titleAsText":"使用 clear 方法"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"规范","title":"规范","isH3":false,"content":"<p>当前版本或者起草中没有这个方法，这个方法在版本 28（2014 年 10 月 14）之前是 ECMAScript 6 起草规范的一部分，但是在起草之后的版本中被移除了。它不在是最终标准的一部分了&nbsp;。</p>"}},{"type":"browser_compatibility","value":{"title":"浏览器兼容性","id":"浏览器兼容性","isH3":false,"query":"javascript.builtins.WeakMap.clear","dataURL":"/zh-CN/docs/Web/JavaScript/Reference/Global_Objects/WeakMap/clear/bcd.json"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"相近","title":"相近","isH3":false,"content":"<ul>\n <li><a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/JavaScript/Reference/Global_Objects/WeakMap\"><code>WeakMap</code></a></li>